data.description:
Charming one-owner home in Yukon with 3 Beds, 2 Baths, and Private Primary Suite! Welcome to this meticulously maintained one-owner home nestled in the heart of Yukon! This delightful residence boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of comfort and style.
You'll immediately notice the warm and inviting atmosphere as you step inside. The open-concept layout creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it an ideal space for both relaxing and entertaining. The living room is bathed in natural light, with a cozy ambiance welcoming you. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a private en-suite bathroom for your convenience and privacy. Whether unwinding after a long day or starting your morning routine, this serene space provides the tranquility you deserve. One of the highlights of this home is the covered front and back porch, perfect for enjoying the outdoors in any weather. Imagine sipping your morning coffee on the front porch while watching the world go by or hosting barbecues on the back patio. Close to local amenities, parks, schools, and shopping, you'll have everything you need within reach. Don't miss the opportunity to own this well-cared-for home in Yukon. Schedule a showing today and make it yours!
